From 767f6ac9cb84defd9aaaa97903bfa5fa7abe67c9 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Fardinmilani <fardin.milani.user@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 24 Jun 2026 23:37:43 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Finish Decision Center: watchlist screener, paper trade
 journal, in-browser alerts

- Add IndexedDB-backed paper trade store (put/load/delete/mark outcome)
- Implement WatchlistScreener: per-symbol Long/Short/risk scoring, source
  health, sort by best Long/Short/highest risk, 60s in-memory cache to
  limit API requests
- Implement PaperTradePanel: save active setup, list/delete/mark trades,
  JSON/CSV export and JSON import, all using Adaptive Price Precision
- Implement BrowserAlertsPanel: price-cross, drawing-touch, score-threshold,
  and risk/reward alerts, all explicitly scoped to 'while this tab is open'
- Add evaluateBrowserAlert, sortWatchRows, paperTradesCsv, labelize helpers
- Style new panels and previously-unstyled simulation/test-grid cards in
  App.css using the existing design tokens
- Verified: eslint clean, vite build succeeds (pure static bundle, no
  backend/server/API routes added)
